{"tid":847134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"打人女記者孔琳琳 兒子被揭遭英國學校開除","createTime":"2018-10-04T03:05:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T10:27:49.000Z","uid":39464,"like":500,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"cfdf2a40624799a1bba551eb7ae5fca14f333fcb","tid":847134,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T03:05:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181004/large/1538620887_adac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181004%2Flarge%2F1538620887_adac.jpg&h=e9e7f454&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國央視女記者孔琳琳大鬧英國保守黨年會關於香港問題的論壇，還打在場義工被捕，在其獲釋後，事件繼續發酵。網上爆出孔琳琳的兒子已被英國學校開除。<br />\n<br />\n10月3日，微博認證為「著名攝影家」的周雁鳴轉發孔琳琳相關微博稱，「她兒子被英國學校開除了」，開除的原因是「逃課成績差不遵守校規」。同時，還指出，在記者攝影圈內，孔琳琳劣跡斑斑。還有消息稱「她兒子在學校打人被開除了，然後她就發瘋了。」意思做出如此舉動，全是因為她兒子。<br />\n<br />\n於英國時間9月30日，英國保守黨人權委員會在伯明翰保守黨年會期間舉行涉港問題會議，邀請戴耀廷、羅冠聰等人參會。在會場旁聽的中國中央電視台歐洲中心站記者孔琳琳提問發言時表達觀點遭到阻撓，她便向在場的義工動粗。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181004/58754201\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181004%2F58754201&d=%2FYputimRECP4bxIM%2BUTwT9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=dbb9af5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181004%2F58754201&h=0a6a247f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181004/58754201</a>"},{"pid":"d07835847c0c5c911825a49eaa53d2b3942e7423","tid":847134,"uid":54337,"like":513,"dislike":3,"score":510,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T03:07:34.000Z","msg":"龍生龍，鳳生鳳，老鼠生來會打洞<br />\n<br />\n銅油埕只可以裝銅油，真係無講錯"},{"pid":"7dcef3291767c6e80db315d38e5a2fa45c7fa878","tid":847134,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T03:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14d